{
  "texts": [
    "Per cell we generated combined expression signatures by adding the negative portal signatures to the central signatures.",
    "Based on these scores clusters in the UMAP were defined to be showing portal or central-specific expression signatures.",
    "For this analysis healthy, regenerating, and embolized tissue hepatocytes were subset individually from the UMAP of combined datasets based on previously annotated cell type markers.",
    "Within each dataset, cells were renormalized using the SCTransform function in Seurat.",
    "Four PCs were then used to project cells in UMAP space."
  ]
}